# Keep Neuron-side Python packages in @neuron_py_deps so `nki-cc` and
# `neuronx-cc` run under Bazel's isolated Python sandbox. On current SDK
# releases `nkilib` is shipped inside the `neuronx-cc` wheel, so we do not pin
# a separate `nki-library` wheel here unless the SDK packaging changes.
